This position provides operational support to the trading team in areas like data research, price monitoring and scheduling of shipments.
1. Provide daily updates on local price
2. Monitor the spread market and CNF disparity
3. Update sales &amp; shipment plan for China market
4. Update daily trade done report
5. Prepare weekly meeting report
6. Liaise with counterparties for shipment schedule
7. Follow up cargo readiness, shipping issues &amp; payment status
8. Assist in yearly Audit
9. Assist in RSPO Book-keeping
Updating daily margin for assigned product and market
